msgctxt "Description|"
msgid "This module offers time series analyses."
msgstr "Modul ini menawarkan analisis seri waktu."

msgctxt "Description|"
msgid "Stationarity"
msgstr "Stasioneritas"

msgctxt "Description|"
msgid "ARIMA"
msgstr "ARIMA"

msgctxt "Description|"
msgid "Spectral Analysis"
msgstr "Analisis Spektral"

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid ""
"Allows the user to fit a (seasonal) AR/MA/ARMA/ARIMA model to a time series."
msgstr ""
"Mengizinkan pengguna untuk menyesuaikan model AR/MA/ARMA/ARIMA (musiman) ke "
"seri waktu."

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "Dependent Variable"
msgstr "Variabel Dependen"

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "A variable that is measured repeatedly over time."
msgstr "Variabel yang diukur secara berulang dari waktu."

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "Time"
msgstr "Waktu"

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid ""
"Optional. Can either be an ordinal variable indicating the time index/order "
"of the observations, or a text variable indicating the date/time stamp of "
"the observations. Combined date and time values should be in the standard "
"format 'YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM:SS', where seconds (':SS') can also be omitted. "
"Date-only values should be in the format 'YYYY-MM-DD'. If a time variable is "
"not supplied, the row order of the data is used."
msgstr ""
"Opsional. Dapat baik variabel ordinal mengindikasikan indeks waktu/urutan "
"observasi, atau variabel teks mengindikasikan tanggal/stempel waktu "
"observasi. Nilai tanggal dan waktu terkombinasi seharusnya dalam format "
"standar 'YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM:SS', di mana detik (':SS') juga dapat dihilangkan. "
"Nilai hanya tanggal seharusnya dalam format 'YYYY-MM-DD'. Jika variabel "
"waktu tidak disertakan, urutan baris data digunakan."

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "Covariates"
msgstr "Kovariat"

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid ""
"Optional. A numerical variable to include in the model as external regressor."
msgstr ""
"Opsional. Variabel numerik untuk disertakan di model sebagai regresor "
"eksternal."

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "Time series plot"
msgstr "Diagram seri waktu"

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "Plots the dependent variable (y-axis) over time (x-axis)."
msgstr "Mendiagram variabel dependen (sumbu-y) terhadap waktu (sumbu-x)."

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "Points"
msgstr "Titik"

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "Line"
msgstr "Garis"

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "Both"
msgstr "Keduanya"

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "Distribution"
msgstr "Distribusi"

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "Density"
msgstr "Kepadatan"

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "Histogram"
msgstr "Histogram"

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "None"
msgstr "Tidak Ada"

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "Filter by"
msgstr "Filter berdasarkan"

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid ""
"Filters the time series so only a specific range will be used for further "
"analyses. Row number refers to the row number in the spreadsheet. If a "
"'Time' variable is supplied it is also possible to filter by time index or "
"date, depending on the format of the 'Time' variable."
msgstr ""
"Menyaring seri waktu sehingga hanya rentang tertentu akan digunakan untuk "
"analisis lebih lanjut. Nomor baris mengacu nomor baris di lembar kerja. Jika "
"variabel 'Waktu' disertakan itu juga dapat menyaring berdasarkan indeks "
"waktu atau tanggal, tergantung pada format variabel 'Waktu'."

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "Row number"
msgstr "Angka baris"

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "Start"
msgstr "Mulai"

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "End"
msgstr "Selesai"

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "Time index"
msgstr "Indeks waktu"

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "Date"
msgstr "Tanggal"

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "Model"
msgstr "Model"

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "Intercept"
msgstr "Intersepsi"

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "Include an intercept in the model."
msgstr "Sertakan intersepsi dalam model."

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "Seasonal components"
msgstr "Komponen musiman"

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid ""
"Fit a seasonal ARIMA model. If the frequency is not known, a dominant "
"frequency may be determined from a spectral analysis."
msgstr ""
"Sesuaikan model ARIMA. Jika frekuensi tidak diketahui, frekuensi dominan "
"mungkin ditentukan dari analisis spektral."

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "Period"
msgstr "Periode"

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "Custom"
msgstr "Kustom"

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "Dominant"
msgstr "Dominan"

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "Model Specification"
msgstr "Spesifikasi Model"

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid ""
"Specifies what ARIMA model to fit. The best fitting model is determined by "
"the Hyndman-Khandakar algorithm."
msgstr ""
"Menentukan apa model ARIMA untuk disesuaikan. Model penyesuaian terbaik "
"ditentukan oleh algoritma Hyndman-Khandakar."

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "Best fitting"
msgstr "Penyesuaian terbaik"

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "Information criterion"
msgstr "Kriteria informasi"

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "AICc"
msgstr "AICc"

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "AIC"
msgstr "AIC"

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "BIC"
msgstr "BIC"

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "Manual"
msgstr "Manual"

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "Nonseasonal"
msgstr "Nonmusiman"

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "Autoregressive (AR) order p"
msgstr "Urutan regresif otomatis (AR) p"

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "Difference (I) degree d"
msgstr "Derajat perbedaan (I) d"

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "Moving average (MA) order q"
msgstr "Urutan rata-rata perpindahan (MA) q"

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "Seasonal"
msgstr "Musiman"

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "Autoregressive (AR) order P"
msgstr "Urutan regresif otomatis (AR) p"

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "Difference (I) degree D"
msgstr "Derajat perbedaan (I) D"

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "Moving average (MA) order Q"
msgstr "Urutan rata-rata perpindahan (MA) q"

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "Residual Diagnostics"
msgstr "Diagnostik Residu"

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "Plots"
msgstr "Diagram"

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "Plots the residuals (y-axis) over time (x-axis)."
msgstr "Mendiagram residu (sumbu-y) terhadap waktu (sumbu-x)."

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "Q-Q plot"
msgstr "Diagram Q-Q"

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "Plots the quantile-quantile plot of the residuals."
msgstr "Mendiagram diagram kuantil-kuantil residu."

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "Autocorrelation"
msgstr "Korelasi Otomatis"

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "Autocorrelation function"
msgstr "Fungsi korelasi otomatis"

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid ""
"Plots the autocorrelation for a specified number of lags. The confidence "
"interval may be given assuming a white noise process."
msgstr ""
"Mendiagram korelasi otomatis untuk jumlah penundaan tertentu. Interval "
"kepercayaan mungkin diberikan mengasumsi proses noise putih."

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "Zero lag"
msgstr "Nol penundaan"

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "Confidence interval"
msgstr "Interval kepercayaan"

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "Ljung-Box p-values"
msgstr "Nilai-p Kotak-Ljung"

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid ""
"Plots the p-values of the Ljung-Box test for a number of lags of which the "
"null hypothesis assumes that the data independently distributed and "
"therefore have no autocorrelation."
msgstr ""
"Mendiagram nilai-p uji Kotak-Ljung untuk jumlah penundaan di mana hipotesis "
"null mengasumsikan bahwa data secara independen didistribusikan dan oleh "
"karena itu tidak memiliki korelasi otomatis."

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "Significance level"
msgstr "Tingkat signifikan"

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "Maximum lag"
msgstr "Penundaan maksimum"

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "Append residuals to spreadsheet"
msgstr "Tambahkan residu ke lembar kerja"

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "Column name"
msgstr "Nama kolom"

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "e.g., residuals"
msgstr "mis., residu"

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "Forecasting"
msgstr "Perkiraan"

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "Number of forecasts"
msgstr "Jumlah perkiraan"

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "Determines the number forecasts to make."
msgstr "Menentukan jumlah perkiraan untuk dibuat."

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "Save forecasts as"
msgstr "Simpan perkiraan sebagai"

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "e.g. forecasts.csv"
msgstr "mis. forecasts.csv"

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "Saves the forecasts in a seperate .csv file."
msgstr "Menyimpan perkiraan dalam berkas .csv terpisah."

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "Plots the forecasts (and observed values) (y-axis) over time (x-axis)"
msgstr ""
"Mendiagram perkiraan (dan nilai terobservasi) (sumbu-y) terhadap waktu "
"(sumbu-x)"

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "Observed data"
msgstr "Data terobservasi"

msgctxt "ARIMATimeSeries|"
msgid "Forecasts table"
msgstr "Tabel perkiraan"

msgctxt "SpectralTimeSeries|"
msgid ""
"Spectral analysis allows the user to assess the frequency components and "
"power distribution of a time series."
msgstr ""
"Analisis spektral mengizinkan pengguna untuk mengevaluasi komponen frekuensi "
"dan distribusi daya seri waktu."

msgctxt "SpectralTimeSeries|"
msgid "Variable"
msgstr "Variabel"

msgctxt "SpectralTimeSeries|"
msgid "A variable that is measured repeatedly over time."
msgstr "Variabel yang diukur secara berulang dari waktu."

msgctxt "SpectralTimeSeries|"
msgid "Time"
msgstr "Waktu"

msgctxt "SpectralTimeSeries|"
msgid ""
"Optional. Can either be an ordinal variable indicating the order of the "
"observations, or a text variable indicating the date/time stamp of the "
"observations. Combined date and time values should be in the standard format "
"'YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM:SS', where seconds (':SS') can also be omitted. Date-only "
"values should be in the format 'YYYY-MM-DD'. If a time variable is not "
"supplied, the row order of the data is used."
msgstr ""
"Opsional. Dapat baik variabel ordinal mengindikasikan urutan observasi, atau "
"variabel teks mengindikasikan tanggal/stempel waktu observasi. Nilai tanggal "
"dan waktu terkombinasi seharusnya dalam format standar 'YYYY-MM-DD "
"HH:MM:SS', di mana detik (':SS') juga dapat dihilangkan. Nilai hanya tanggal "
"seharusnya dalam format 'YYYY-MM-DD'. Jika variabel waktu tidak disertakan, "
"urutan baris data digunakan."

msgctxt "SpectralTimeSeries|"
msgid "Spectral density"
msgstr "Kepadatan spektral"

msgctxt "SpectralTimeSeries|"
msgid "Kernel smoother"
msgstr "Pelembut kernel"

msgctxt "SpectralTimeSeries|"
msgid ""
"Smooths the power spectral density using a kernel. The dimension determines "
"the convolution of kernels. The taper specifies the proportion of data to "
"which a split cosine bell taper is applied at the beginning and end of the "
"series."
msgstr ""
"Menghaluskan kepadatan spektral daya menggunakan kernel. Dimensi menentukan "
"konvolusi kernel. Taper menentukan proporsi data yang di mana taper lonceng "
"kosinus terpisah diterapkan di awal dan akhir seri."

msgctxt "SpectralTimeSeries|"
msgid "Daniell"
msgstr "Daniell"

msgctxt "SpectralTimeSeries|"
msgid "Modified Daniell"
msgstr "Daniell Termodifikasi"

msgctxt "SpectralTimeSeries|"
msgid "Dimension"
msgstr "Dimensi"

msgctxt "SpectralTimeSeries|"
msgid "Term "
msgstr "Istilah "

msgctxt "SpectralTimeSeries|"
msgid "Taper"
msgstr "Taper"

msgctxt "SpectralTimeSeries|"
msgid "Filter by"
msgstr "Filter berdasarkan"

msgctxt "SpectralTimeSeries|"
msgid ""
"Filters the time series so only a specific range will be used for further "
"analyses. Row number refers to the row number in the spreadsheet. If a "
"'Time' variable is supplied it is also possible to filter by time index or "
"date, depending on the format of the 'Time' variable."
msgstr ""
"Menyaring seri waktu sehingga hanya rentang tertentu akan digunakan untuk "
"analisis lebih lanjut. Nomor baris mengacu nomor baris di lembar kerja. Jika "
"variabel 'Waktu' disertakan itu juga dapat menyaring berdasarkan indeks "
"waktu atau tanggal, tergantung pada format variabel 'Waktu'."

msgctxt "SpectralTimeSeries|"
msgid "Row number"
msgstr "Angka baris"

msgctxt "SpectralTimeSeries|"
msgid "Start"
msgstr "Mulai"

msgctxt "SpectralTimeSeries|"
msgid "End"
msgstr "Selesai"

msgctxt "SpectralTimeSeries|"
msgid "Time index"
msgstr "Indeks waktu"

msgctxt "SpectralTimeSeries|"
msgid "Date"
msgstr "Tanggal"

msgctxt "SpectralTimeSeries|"
msgid "Noise shape line"
msgstr "Garis bentuk noise"

msgctxt "SpectralTimeSeries|"
msgid ""
"Add a line to the spectral density indicating the power spectral density of "
"a white, pink or brown noise process."
msgstr ""
"Tambahkan garis ke kepadatan spektral mengindikasikan kepadatan spektral "
"daya proses noise putih, merah muda, atau cokelat."

msgctxt "SpectralTimeSeries|"
msgid "White noise"
msgstr "Noise putih"

msgctxt "SpectralTimeSeries|"
msgid "Pink noise"
msgstr "Noise merah muda"

msgctxt "SpectralTimeSeries|"
msgid "Brown noise"
msgstr "Noise cokelat"

msgctxt "SpectralTimeSeries|"
msgid "Transformation"
msgstr "Transformasi"

msgctxt "SpectralTimeSeries|"
msgid "Transforms the time series by removing the trend or mean."
msgstr "Mentransformasikan seri waktu dengan menghapus tren atau rerata."

msgctxt "SpectralTimeSeries|"
msgid "Detrend"
msgstr "Detren"

msgctxt "SpectralTimeSeries|"
msgid "Demean"
msgstr "Dererata"

msgctxt "StationarityTimeSeries|"
msgid ""
"Stationarity allows the user to test a univariate time-series for "
"stationarity and to transform the time-series if necessary."
msgstr ""
"Stasioneritas mengizinkan pengguna untuk menguji seri waktu univariat untuk "
"stasioneritas dan untuk mentransformasikan seri waktu jika diperlukan."

msgctxt "StationarityTimeSeries|"
msgid "Variable"
msgstr "Variabel"

msgctxt "StationarityTimeSeries|"
msgid "A variable that is measured repeatedly over time."
msgstr "Variabel yang diukur secara berulang dari waktu."

msgctxt "StationarityTimeSeries|"
msgid "Time"
msgstr "Waktu"

msgctxt "StationarityTimeSeries|"
msgid ""
"Optional. Can either be an ordinal variable indicating the order of the "
"observations, or a text variable indicating the date/time stamp of the "
"observations. Combined date and time values should be in the standard format "
"'YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM:SS', where seconds (':SS') can also be omitted. Date-only "
"values should be in the format 'YYYY-MM-DD'. If a time variable is not "
"supplied, the row order of the data is used."
msgstr ""
"Opsional. Dapat baik variabel ordinal mengindikasikan urutan observasi, atau "
"variabel teks mengindikasikan tanggal/stempel waktu observasi. Nilai tanggal "
"dan waktu terkombinasi seharusnya dalam format standar 'YYYY-MM-DD "
"HH:MM:SS', di mana detik (':SS') juga dapat dihilangkan. Nilai hanya tanggal "
"seharusnya dalam format 'YYYY-MM-DD'. Jika variabel waktu tidak disertakan, "
"urutan baris data digunakan."

msgctxt "StationarityTimeSeries|"
msgid "Stationarity Tests"
msgstr "Uji Stasioneritas"

msgctxt "StationarityTimeSeries|"
msgid "Augmented Dickey-Fuller"
msgstr "Dickey-Fuller Teraugmentasi"

msgctxt "StationarityTimeSeries|"
msgid "Phillips-Perron"
msgstr "Phillips-Perron"

msgctxt "StationarityTimeSeries|"
msgid ""
"Computes a PP test where the null assumes that the time-series has a unit "
"root. The p-values are interpolated from a table of critical values in "
"Banerjee et al. (1993), when the statistic lies outside the range of "
"critical values, a note is added to the table."
msgstr ""
"Menghitung uji PP di mana null mengasumsikan bahwa seri waktu memiliki akar "
"unit. Nilai-p diinterpolasikan dari tabel nilai kritis di Banerjee et al. "
"(1993), ketika statistik berada di luar rentang nilai kritis, catatan "
"ditambahkan ke tabel."

msgctxt "StationarityTimeSeries|"
msgid "Regression coefficient test"
msgstr "Uji koefisien regresi"

msgctxt "StationarityTimeSeries|"
msgid "Studentized test"
msgstr "Uji terstudent"

msgctxt "StationarityTimeSeries|"
msgid "Kwiatkowski-Phillips-Schmidt-Shin"
msgstr "Kwiatkowski-Phillips-Schmidt-Shin"

msgctxt "StationarityTimeSeries|"
msgid ""
"Computes a KPSS test where the null assumes that the time-series is level or "
"trend stationary. The p-values are interpolated from a table of critical "
"values in Kwiatkowski et al. (1992), when the statistic lies outside the "
"range of critical values, a note is added to the table."
msgstr ""
"Menghitun uji KPSS di mana null mengasumsikan bahwa seri waktu adalah "
"stasioner tingkat atau tren. Nilai-p diinterpolasikan dari tabel nilai "
"kritis di Kwiatkowski et al. (1992), ketika statistik berada di luar rentang "
"nilai kritis, catata ditambahkan ke tabel."

msgctxt "StationarityTimeSeries|"
msgid "Level stationary"
msgstr "Stasioner tingkat"

msgctxt "StationarityTimeSeries|"
msgid "Trend stationary"
msgstr "Stasioner tren"

msgctxt "StationarityTimeSeries|"
msgid "Filter by"
msgstr "Filter berdasarkan"

msgctxt "StationarityTimeSeries|"
msgid ""
"Filters the time series so only a specific range will be used for further "
"analyses. Row number refers to the row number in the spreadsheet. If a "
"'Time' variable is supplied it is also possible to filter by time index or "
"date, depending on the format of the 'Time' variable."
msgstr ""
"Menyaring seri waktu sehingga hanya rentang tertentu akan digunakan untuk "
"analisis lebih lanjut. Nomor baris mengacu nomor baris di lembar kerja. Jika "
"variabel 'Waktu' disertakan itu juga dapat menyaring berdasarkan indeks "
"waktu atau tanggal, tergantung pada format variabel 'Waktu'."

msgctxt "StationarityTimeSeries|"
msgid "Row number"
msgstr "Angka baris"

msgctxt "StationarityTimeSeries|"
msgid "Start"
msgstr "Mulai"

msgctxt "StationarityTimeSeries|"
msgid "End"
msgstr "Selesai"

msgctxt "StationarityTimeSeries|"
msgid "Time index"
msgstr "Indeks waktu"

msgctxt "StationarityTimeSeries|"
msgid "Date"
msgstr "Tanggal"

msgctxt "StationarityTimeSeries|"
msgid "Transformation"
msgstr "Transformasi"

msgctxt "StationarityTimeSeries|"
msgid "Log"
msgstr "Log"

msgctxt "StationarityTimeSeries|"
msgid "Takes the log of the dependent variable."
msgstr "Mengambil log variabel dependen."

msgctxt "StationarityTimeSeries|"
msgid "Base 10"
msgstr "Basis 10"

msgctxt "StationarityTimeSeries|"
msgid "Base e"
msgstr "Basis e"

msgctxt "StationarityTimeSeries|"
msgid "Root"
msgstr "Akar"

msgctxt "StationarityTimeSeries|"
msgid "Takes the root of the dependent variable."
msgstr "Mengambil akar variabel dependen."

msgctxt "StationarityTimeSeries|"
msgid "Square"
msgstr "Persegi"

msgctxt "StationarityTimeSeries|"
msgid "Cube"
msgstr "Kubus"

msgctxt "StationarityTimeSeries|"
msgid "Box-Cox"
msgstr "Box-Cox"

msgctxt "StationarityTimeSeries|"
msgid ""
"Transforms the dependent variable using a Box-Cox transformation. Lambda is "
"the transformation parameter. If lambda is chosen automatically, it "
"minimizes the coefficient of variation for the dependent variable using "
"Guerrero's method."
msgstr ""
"Mentransformasikan variabel dependen menggunakan transformasi Box-Cox. "
"Lambda adalah parameter transformasi. Jika lambda dipilih secara otomatis, "
"itu meminimalkan koefisien variasi untuk variabel dependen menggunakan "
"metode Guerrero."

msgctxt "StationarityTimeSeries|"
msgid "Lambda"
msgstr "Lambda"

msgctxt "StationarityTimeSeries|"
msgid "Auto"
msgstr "Otomatis"

msgctxt "StationarityTimeSeries|"
msgid "Custom"
msgstr "Kustom"

msgctxt "StationarityTimeSeries|"
msgid "Detrend using linear regression"
msgstr "Detren menggunakan regresi linear"

msgctxt "StationarityTimeSeries|"
msgid ""
"Fits a polynomial regression to the dependent variable with time as "
"predictor, and keeps only the residuals. If best fitting is selected, the "
"polynomial regression is chosen based on the information criterion."
msgstr ""
"Menyesuaikan regresi polinomial ke variabel dependen dengan waktu sebagai "
"prediktor, dan menjaga hanya residu. Jika penyesuaian terbaik dipilih, "
"regresi polinomial dipilih berdasarkan kriteria informasi."

msgctxt "StationarityTimeSeries|"
msgid "Polynomial"
msgstr "Polinomial"

msgctxt "StationarityTimeSeries|"
msgid "Best fitting"
msgstr "Penyesuaian terbaik"

msgctxt "StationarityTimeSeries|"
msgid "Maximum"
msgstr "Maksimum"

msgctxt "StationarityTimeSeries|"
msgid "Information criterion"
msgstr "Kriteria informasi"

msgctxt "StationarityTimeSeries|"
msgid "AIC"
msgstr "AIC"

msgctxt "StationarityTimeSeries|"
msgid "BIC"
msgstr "BIC"

msgctxt "StationarityTimeSeries|"
msgid "Difference"
msgstr "Perbedaan"

msgctxt "StationarityTimeSeries|"
msgid ""
"Differences the dependent variable. Note that differencing leads to a "
"shorter time-series (n - lag) as a lag is used."
msgstr ""
"Membedakan variabel dependen. Catat bahwa membedakan menyebabkan seri waktu "
"lebih pendek (n - lag) karena penundaan digunakan."

msgctxt "StationarityTimeSeries|"
msgid "Lag"
msgstr "Penundaan"

msgctxt "StationarityTimeSeries|"
msgid "Order"
msgstr "Urutan"

msgctxt "StationarityTimeSeries|"
msgid "Append transformation to spreadsheet"
msgstr "Tambahkan transformasi ke lembar kerja"

msgctxt "StationarityTimeSeries|"
msgid ""
"Appends the transformed dependent variable to the spreadsheet, so these can "
"be used in further analyses."
msgstr ""
"Menambahkan variabel dependen tertransformasi ke lembar kerja, jadi ini "
"dapat digunakan dalam analisis masa mendatang."

msgctxt "StationarityTimeSeries|"
msgid "Column name"
msgstr "Nama kolom"

msgctxt "StationarityTimeSeries|"
